lag mf trend data

Source: R/mf_lag_trend.R
mf_lag_trend.Rd

Creates twelve month lag, three month sum, lagged by twelve months, and twelve month sum, lagged by 12 months.

mf_lag_trend(x = trend)

Arguments

x

A data frame with columns for "cdi", "ecoli", "mrsa", "mssa", "kleb", "paer" and "ecoli_ta".

Value

The same dataframe, but with new lagged variables added

Examples

library(dplyr)
